d%2Fvaccines%2Fstay-up-to-date.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20CDC%20website%20%3C%2Fa%3Eat%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222da6a348-928b-409c-8cf0-a0f49aa16ee2%5C%22%3EOB-GYNs%20are%20pushing%20back%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20policy%20will%20mean%20that%20the%20COVID-19%20vaccine%20is%20only%20recommended%20to%20people%20older%20than%2065%20and%20those%20at%20high%20risk%20for%20severe%20COVID-19.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20a%20group%20that%20should%20%E2%80%94%20and%20does%20%E2%80%94%20include%20all%20pregnant%20women%2C%20according%20to%20obstetricians%2C%20professional%20associations%2C%20and%20even%20Dr.%20Marty%20Makary%2C%20the%20newly%20appointed%20commissioner%20of%20the%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20(FDA).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Makary%20included%20pregnancy%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1056%2FNEJMsb2506929%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20England%20Journal%20of%20Medicine%3C%2Fa%3E%20article%20listing%20medical%20conditions%20that%20would%20put%20someone%20at%20higher%20risk%20for%20the%20disease%2C%20alongside%20asthma%20and%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20OB-GYN%20in%20this%20country%20that%20I%20know%20who%20is%20in%20agreement%20with%20this%20recommendation%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Amanda%20Williams%2C%20a%20practicing%20obstetrician-gynecologist%20in%20northern%20California%2C%20who%20is%20the%20interim%20chief%20medical%20officer%20at%20March%20of%20Dimes%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BPregnancy%20is%20a%20high-risk%20condition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pregnant%20woman%20drinking%20cup%20of%20tea%20in%20the%20sun.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b890577bb3f854015d76c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223446%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20FDA%20commissioner%20put%20pregnancy%20(and%20recent%20pregnancy)%20on%20a%20list%20of%20underlying%20medical%20conditions%20that%20increase%20a%20person's%20risk%20of%20severe%20COVID-19.%3Cp%3EKathrin%20Ziegler%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20says%20people%20should%20ignore%20the%20latest%20government%20recommendation%2C%20and%20continue%20to%20follow%20the%20advice%20of%20professional%20associations%2C%20including%20the%20American%20Academy%20of%20Pediatrics%2C%20and%20the%20American%20College%20of%20Obstetricians%20and%20Gynecologists%2C%20which%20both%20continue%20to%20recommend%20COVID-19%20vaccines%20to%20pregnant%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BACOG's%20recommendations%20have%20not%20changed%20as%20the%20science%20has%20not%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20organization%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPregnancy%20suppresses%20the%20immune%20system%2C%20making%20people%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20infectious%20diseases%20like%20COVID.%20Pregnancy%20also%20prompts%20widespread%20changes%20to%20a%20person's%20vascular%20system%20and%20respiration%2C%20which%20can%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20a%20pregnant%20body%20to%20fight%20off%20the%20virus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20patients%20have%20COVID%2C%20they%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20have%20miscarriage%2C%20stillbirth%2C%20preeclampsia%2C%20and%20preterm%20birth%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20patient%20gets%20COVID%20and%20is%20pregnant%2C%20they're%20more%20likely%20to%20need%20to%20be%20hospitalized%2C%20intubated%2C%20and%20unfortunately%20die%20because%20of%20COVID.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20remembers%20the%20case%20of%20a%20healthy%2C%20young%20mother-to-be%20who%20contracted%20COVID%20during%20the%20height%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20had%20to%20be%20intubated%2C%20and%20ultimately%20died%2C%20a%20few%20days%20after%20giving%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20very%20last%20thing%20that%20she%20said%20to%20the%20obstetric%20team%20was%2C%20'I%20wish%20I%20had%20gotten%20the%20vaccination%20and%20not%20listened%20to%20other%20people%2C'%26quot%3B%20Williams%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20rumors%20online%20that%20COVID-19%20vaccines%20mess%20with%20fertility%20and%20can%20cause%20miscarriages.%20Even%20though%20the%20claims%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcoronavirus.delaware.gov%2Fcovid-19-myth-or-fact%2Fmyth-or-fact-the-covid-19-vaccine-causes-infertility%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewidely%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fcovid%2Fvaccines%2Fpregnant-or-breastfeeding.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediscredited%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20persist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20person%20who's%20been%20pregnant%20before%20knows%20it's%20really%20hard%20to%20get%20a%20deep%20breath%20and%20to%20walk%20up%20and%20down%20stairs%2C%20even%20in%20normal%20pregnancy%20%E2%80%94%20imagine%20what%20that's%20like%20then%20with%20COVID%20on%20top%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20made%20it%20my%20personal%20mission%20to%20be%20vocal%2C%20especially%20in%20communities%20of%20color%20%E2%80%94%20where%20there%20is%20well-earned%20distrust%20%E2%80%94%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20vaccine%2C%20what%20the%20safety%20data%20has%20shown%20us%2C%20and%20to%20try%20to%20be%20a%20trusted%20messenger%20and%20bridge%20builder%20so%20that%20things%20like%20that%20wouldn't%20happen%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20given%20during%20the%20second%20or%20third%20trimester%20of%20pregnancy%2C%20vaccines%20can%20also%20help%20protect%20a%20newborn%20baby%20from%20COVID%20for%20roughly%20their%20first%20six%20months%20of%20life%2C%20through%20the%20transfer%20of%20maternal%20antibodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20existing%20data%20shows%20that%20these%20vaccines%20can%20help%20protect%20children%20and%20they%20can%20help%20protect%20pregnant%20women%20and%20they%20can%20help%20protect%20even%20infants%20after%20they're%20born%2C%26quot%3B%20Jesse%20Goodman%2C%20a%20former%20FDA%20chief%20scientist%20who%20is%20now%20director%20of%20Georgetown%20University's%20Center%20on%20Medical%20Product%20Access%2C%20Safety%20and%20Stewardship%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statnews.com%2F2025%2F05%2F27%2Fcovid-shots-pregnant-women-children-recommendation-change-hhs-secretary-kennedy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESTAT%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20pretty%20taken%20aback%20by%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frfk-ends-vaccine-recommendation-for-kids-pregnant-people-maha-moms-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748465902000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683765cfca50259add4d3bfc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frfk-ends-vaccine-recommendation-for-kids-pregnant-people-maha-moms-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20COVID-19%20vaccine%20won't%20be%20recommended%20to%20pregnant%20people%20or%20healthy%20children%20in%20the%20US%20anymore.%20Doctors%20weigh%20in.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kschewitz%40businessinsider.com%20(Kim%20Schewitz%2CHilary%20Brueck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A146%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frfk-ends-vaccine-recommendation-for-kids-pregnant-people-maha-moms-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20wants%20Congress%20to%20approve%20%249%20billion%20in%20DOGE%20cuts%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20including%20more%20than%20%241%20billion%20in%20cuts%20to%20public%20broadcasting%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e0926c6ad288d14807c9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20wants%20Congress%20to%20approve%20a%20series%20of%20DOGE's%20cuts.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Moneymaker%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20is%20aiming%20for%20Congress%20to%20push%20through%20billions%20in%20DOGE%20spending%20cuts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20package%20includes%20cuts%20to%20the%20Corporation%20for%20Public%20Broadcasting%20and%20USAID%2C%20per%20an%20OMB%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20%249.4%20billion%20represents%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20roughly%20%24150%20billion%20that%20DOGE%20said%20it%20has%20saved.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20wants%20to%20make%20some%20DOGE%20cuts%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20will%20send%20a%20%249.4%20billion%20rescissions%20package%20to%20Congress%20next%20week%2C%20giving%20Republicans%20an%20opportunity%20to%20enact%20cuts%20suggested%20by%20Elon%20Musk's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-department-of-government-efficiency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWhite%20House%20DOGE%20office%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Office%20of%20Management%20and%20Budget%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20package%20will%20include%20%241.1%20billion%20in%20cuts%20to%20the%20Corporation%20for%20Public%20Broadcasting%20and%20%248.3%20billion%20in%20spending%20reductions%20to%20foreign%20aid%20at%20the%20US%20Agency%20for%20International%20Development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20is%20aiming%20stop%20the%20CPB%20from%20funding%20PBS%20and%20NPR%2C%20which%20was%20the%20subject%20of%20an%20executive%20order%20that%20he%20issued%20earlier%20this%20month.%20The%20president%20has%20long%20targeted%20funding%20for%20public%20broadcasting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%249.4%20billion%20in%20spending%20reductions%20is%20far%20below%20where%20many%