work%20that%20the%20DOGE%20team%20is%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20during%20the%20interview.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20vote%20can%20be%20big%2C%20or%20it%20could%20be%20beautiful.%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20it%20could%20be%20both.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-media-blitz-summary-doge-white-house-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erecent%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20The%20Washington%20Post%2C%20Musk%20also%20said%20it's%20an%20%26quot%3Buphill%20battle%20trying%20to%20improve%20things%26quot%3B%20in%20Washington%20%E2%80%94%20as%20he%20spoke%20about%20the%20backlash%20that%20DOGE%20has%20so%20far%20faced%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDOGE%20is%20just%20becoming%20the%20whipping%20boy%20for%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20newspaper.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20like%2C%20something%20bad%20would%20happen%20anywhere%2C%20and%20we%20would%20get%20blamed%20for%20it%20even%20if%20we%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-congress-doge-spending-cuts-pbs-npr-rescissions-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748465542000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6837734e6ffb6822ec61b0d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-congress-doge-spending-cuts-pbs-npr-rescissions-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20OMB%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20package%20will%20include%20%241.1%20billion%20in%20cuts%20to%20the%20Corporation%20for%20Public%20Broadcasting.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(John%20L.%20Dorman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A224%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-congress-doge-spending-cuts-pbs-npr-rescissions-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampU