Peter%2C%20who%20proclaims%20his%20love%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMid-gala%2C%20Peter%20ends%20his%2013-year%20marriage%20to%20Michaela%20and%20starts%20a%20relationship%20with%20Simone%2C%20who%20he%20believes%20will%20bring%20%26quot%3Blove%20and%20light%26quot%3B%20into%20his%20life%20(and%20maybe%20even%20another%20child).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimone%20then%20morphs%20into%20Michaela%202.0%2C%20adopting%20her%20cultlike%20mannerisms%20and%20embracing%20her%20new%20position%20of%20power%20at%20the%20estate.%20She%20and%20Devon%20have%20an%20emotional%20goodbye%2C%20knowing%20that%20they're%20embarking%20on%20completely%20different%20paths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20ferry%20ride%20out%20of%20Port%20Haven%2C%20Devon%20runs%20into%20Michaela%2C%20who's%20been%20ousted%20from%20Cliff%20House%20and%20has%20no%20idea%20where%20she's%20headed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDevon%20apologizes%20for%20accusing%20Michaela%20of%20being%20a%20murderer%20and%20a%20cult%20leader%2C%20and%20Michaela%20accepts%20her%20apology%20and%20encourages%20Devon%20to%20cash%20the%20%2410%2C000%20check%20she%20gave%20her%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20series%20so%20she%20can%20fund%20a%20better%20life%20for%20herself%20in%20Buffalo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20series%20concludes%20with%20Simone%2C%20wearing%20an%20elegant%20light-blue%20gown%20that%20Michaela%20got%20her%20for%20the%20gala%2C%20standing%20at%20the%20cliff%2C%20staring%20at%20the%20vista%20during%20sunset%20with%20the%20hint%20of%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2208fd32c9-7c1f-4d03-b534-6762cbce63c6%5C%22%3EWill%20'Sirens'%20return%20for%20season%20two%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Milly%20Alcock%20as%20Simone%20in%20%26quot%3BSirens.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68375d7bca50259add4d3a67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMilly%20Alcock%20as%20Simone%20in%20%26quot%3BSirens.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix