t%2C%20a%20luxury%20home%20design%20and%20fragrance%20brand.%3Cp%3EL'Objet%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20Creative%20Ventures%2C%20a%20series%20about%20business%20success%20rooted%20in%20creativity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20luxury%20home%20design%20and%20fragrance%20brand%20L'Objet%20boasts%20an%20elegant%20boutique%20on%20New%20York%20City's%20Madison%20Avenue.%20The%20space%2C%20bathed%20in%20earthy%20hues%2C%20harmoniously%20blends%20handcrafted%20housewares%2C%20decorative%20items%2C%20and%20scents%20from%20the%20company's%20various%20collections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20two%20decades%2C%20L'Objet's%20founder%20and%20creative%20director%2C%20Elad%20Yifrach%2C%20has%20sustained%20the%20business%20on%20craftsmanship%20and%20creativity.%20In%20celebration%20of%20its%2020th%20anniversary%2C%20the%20brand%20recently%20released%20a%20collection%20of%20nature-inspired%20objets%20(%26quot%3Bobjects%26quot%3B%20in%20French)%2C%20including%20a%20gold-plated%20ladybug%20bottle%20opener%20and%20a%20glazed%20porcelain%20bowl%20designed%20to%20resemble%20cenote%20wavelets.%20It%20also%20expanded%20its%20fragrance%20line%20in%20early%20May%2C%20dropping%20a%20new%20eau%20de%20parfum%20called%20Blindfold%2C%20created%20with%20the%20master%20perfumer%20Yann%20Vasnier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYifrach%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Portugal%2C%20draws%20inspiration%20from%20his%20Mediterranean-influenced%20upbringing%20and%20international%20travels%20to%20places%20such%20as%20France%2C%20Morocco%2C%20and%20India.%20Globetrotting%20has%20connected%20him%20to%20artisans%20around%20the%20world%2C%20forging%20collaborations%20with%20the%20contemporary%20artist%20Ruan%20Hoffmann%20and%20the%20sculpting%20duo%20the%20Haas%20Brothers%2C%20among%20others.%20The%20brand%20has%20also%20opened%20flagship%20boutiques%20in%20major%20cities%2C%20including%20Paris%2C%20London%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vogue.in%2Fcontent%2Fluxury-brand-lobjets-first-indian-store-in-delhi-has-a-sweet-desi-connection%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20recently%2C%20New%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22L'Objet's%20home%20decor%2C%20housewares%2C%20and%20fragrances%20line%20the%20walls%20at%20the%20company's%20New%20York%20City%20boutique.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683736f5ca50259add4d32d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EL'Objet's%20boutique%20in%20New%20York%20City%20showcases%20items%20such%20as%20dinnerware%2C%20glassware%2C%20and%20decorative%20pieces.%3Cp%3EBrea%20Cubit%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EGrowing%20a%20luxury%20business%20is%20no%20easy%20feat%2C%20Yifrach%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20He%20said%20entrepreneurs%20need%20to%20self-advocate%20and%20have%20a%20clear%20vision%20of%20their%20brand%20identity%20and%20target%20audience.%20%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20matter%20how%20great%20your%20idea%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20a%20video%20call%20from%20L'Objet's%20Portugal%20office.%20%26quot%3BYou%20still%20need%20to%20carve%20a%20space%20for%20yourself%20in%20the%20market%20and%20convince%20the%20market%20that%20you're%20worthy%20of%20that%20space%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20takes%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYifrach%20founded%20L'Objet%20in%202005%20when%20he%20was%20in%20his%20mid-20s%2C%20working%20as%20an%20interior%20designer%20in%20Beverly%20Hills%20and%20developing%20an%20interest%20in%20handmade%20decorative%20pieces.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20very%20young%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20the%20brand%20came%20from%20a%20more%20humble%20and%20naive%20place%20of%20just%20wanting%20to%20create%2C%20experiment%20with%20different%20materials%2C%20and%20learn%20a%20lot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeveloping%20his%20luxury%20label%20required%20a%20%26quot%3Bcrazy%20amount%20of%20legwork%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20In%20the%20early%20aughts%2C%20social%20media%20wasn't%20a%20commerce-driving%20juggernaut%20yet%2C%20and%20online%20shopping%20was%20inferior%20to%20coveted%20shelf%20space%20in%20brick-and-mortar%20stores.%20Digital%20marketing%20and%20virtual%20networking%20were%20also%20still%20ripening%2C%20so%20Yifrach%20said%20he%20had%20to%20rely%20on%20face%20time%20%E2%80%94%20not%20FaceTime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223858%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22L'Objet%20hand%20and%20body%20soap%20samples%20and%20bottles%20lined%20up%20near%20a%20sink%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68373a5a6ffb6822ec61a552%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222572%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShoppers%20at%20L'Objet's%20NYC%20store%20can%20try%20samples%20of%20the%20brand's%20hand%20and%20body%20soaps.%3Cp%3EBrea%20Cubit%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20met%20with%20skilled%20artisans%20to%20learn%20techniques%20for%20making%20stylish%2C%20high-quality%20housewares%2C%20attended%20events%20to%20spread%20the%20word%20about%20L'Objet%2C%20and%20presented%20products%20to%20stores%20to%20sell%20as%20merchandise.%20His%20first-ever%20store%20client%20was%20Bergdorf%20Goodman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYifrach%20said%20he%20had%20moments%20of%20doubt%20even%20as%20his%20company%20gained%20momentum.%20He%20remembers%20opting%20out%20of%20a%20major%20trade%20show%20so%20that%20he%20could%20afford%20to%20open%20L'Objet's%20first%20New%20York%20showroom%20in%202010%2C%20but%20he%20didn't%20get%20very%20many%20visitors%20initially.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20crickets.%20It%20was%20really%20scary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20admitted.%20Every%20time%20he%20heard%20the%20%26quot%3Bding%26quot%3B%20of%20a%20nearby%20elevator%2C%20he'd%20jump%20from%20his%20chair%2C%20thinking%20someone%20had%20arrived%20to%20check%20out%20the%20space.%20But%20investing%20in%20the%20showroom%20gave%20the%20company%20a%20stronger%20identity%2C%20which%20helped%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20Yifrach%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%2020%20years%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20has%20accomplished%20eight-figure%20growth%20and%20aims%20to%20double%20its%20revenue%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20years.%20Direct-to-consumer%20channels%20such%20as%20e-commerce%20and%20retail%20have%20been%20the%20biggest%20growth%20areas%20so%20far%20this%20year%2C%20partially%20due%20to%20new%20boutique%20openings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225034%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20display%20in%20L'Objet's%20NYC%20boutique%20showcases%20glassware%20and%20ceramic%20bowls.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68374b00c6ad288d14821473%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223356%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EL'Objet%20items%20often%20have%20organic%20shapes%20that%20reflect%20Yifrach's%20affinity%20for%20nature.%20%3Cp%3EBrea%20Cubit%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20landscape%20of%20luxury%20brand-building%20has%20changed%20substantially%20since%20Yifrach%20founded%20L'Objet.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshopify-exec-omnichannel-commerce-is-the-new-norm-for-the-retail-sector-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOmnichannel%20marketing%20is%20king%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20cutting%20through%20the%20algorithmic%20clutter%20to%20reach%20%E2%80%94%20and%20resonate%20with%20%E2%80%94%20consumers%20is%20crucial.%20Virality%20isn't%20always%20dependable%2C%20and%20longevity%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20come%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20overnight%20successes%20that%20have%20an%20identity%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20Yifrach%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20identity%20was%20never%20formed%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20just%20a%20lot%20of%20fluff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArtisanship%20and%20timeless%20aesthetics%20are%20two%20pillars%20that%20have%20helped%20sustain%20L'Objet%2C%20even%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiddle-class-economy-wealth-luxury-shopping-consumers-spending-retail-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evolatile%20luxury%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Yifrach%20said.%20Sacrificing%20quality%20to%20create%20products%20that%20capitalize%20on%20trends%20might%20work%20temporarily%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20set%20a%20business%20up%20for%20long-term%20success%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYifrach%20noted%20that%20luxury%20consumers%20nowadays%20are%20especially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fall-inclusives-save-money-have-fun-recession-budgeting-trends-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eselective%20about%20their%20purchases%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20just%20buying%20things%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20buying.%20They%20want%20to%20know%20what%20they're%20getting%20and%20why%20it's%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBrands%20need%20to%20be%20ready%20with%20the%20right%20answers.%20You%20have%20to%20justify%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EL'Objet's%20CEO%2C%20Stanislas%20Le%20Bert%2C%20shared%20a%20similar%20sentiment.%20%26quot%3BConsumers%20are%20more%20educated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI%20during%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20brand's%20Manhattan%20showroom.%20%26quot%3BThey%20want%20to%20understand%20the%20story%20and%20the%20'why'%20behind%20the%20price.%20They%20expect%20transparency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224160%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20headshot%20of%20Stanislas%20Le%20Bert%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6837432ec6ad288d14821348%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223120%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStanislas%20Le%20Bert%20became%20the%20CEO%20of%20L'Objet%20in%202024.%3Cp%3EL'Objet%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHannah%20Reed%2C%20a%20research%20manager%20at%20the%20market%20research%20agency%20Walnut%20Unlimited%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-fashion-colla