rmers%20irrigate%20hope%20in%20the%20village%20of%20Pachegaon%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20visit%20Beed%20in%20October%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20most%20likely%20see%20scores%20of%20farmers%20packing%20their%20lives%20into%20%3Cem%3Epotlis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(cloth%20bags)%20as%20they%20prepare%20for%20their%20sojourn%20to%20Kolhapur%2C%20and%20other%20sugarcane-centric%20regions%20of%20western%20Maharashtra.%20They%20bid%20their%20children%20and%20the%20elderly%20a%20tearful%20goodbye%2C%20knowing%20full%20well%20the%20fate%20they%20are%20resigning%20themselves%20to%20for%20the%20next%20few%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20sugarcane%20factories%2C%20the%20farmers%20live%20in%20makeshift%20shanties%2C%20toil%20for%2015-hour%20stretches%20%E2%80%94%20work%20starts%20at%204%20am%20and%20goes%20on%20till%207%20pm%2C%20breaking%20for%20lunch%20in%20between.%20Their%20hands%20get%20sore%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F245335%2Ffarmer-earns-lakhs-how-to-grow-sugarcane-water-conservation-amar-patil-sangli-award-winning-farmer-innovation-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehacking%20the%20stem%20of%20the%20cane%20with%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekoyta%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E(machete-style%20knife)%2C%20following%20which%20they%20bundle%20the%20cane%2C%20load%20it%20onto%20their%20heads%20and%20carry%20it%20to%20the%20tractor.%C2%A0While%20at%20the%20site%2C%20the%20workers%20are%20expected%20to%20see%20to%20their%20medical%20problems%20and%20expenses.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20season%2C%20many%20farmers%20return%20to%20their%20villages%20in%20Marathwada%20with%20around%20%E2%82%B91%20lakh%20in%20hand%20%E2%80%94%20the%20result%20of%20months%20of%20exhausting%20labour.%20But%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20bring%20back%20money.%20They%20come%20home%20carrying%20fatigue%2C%20stress%2C%20and%20many%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20worrying%20among%20them%20is%20the%20rise%20in%20alcoholism.%20According%20to%20Rajshri%20Deshpande%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20Nabhangan%20Foundation%2C%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20surprising.%20She%20points%20to%20the%20long%2C%20punishing%20hours%20at%20sugarcane%20factories%20and%20the%20physical%20and%20mental%20strain%20that%20comes%20with%20it.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20stench%20of%20the%20sugarcane%2C%20the%20relentless%20pace%20of%20the%20work%20%E2%80%94%20it%20wears%20them%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20With%20little%20rest%2C%20no%20comfort%2C%20and%20nothing%20to%20look%20forward%20to%2C%20many%20workers%20turn%20to%20alcohol%20as%20the%20only%20escape%20they%20can%20find.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20alcoholism%2C%20too%2C%20several%20problems%20plague%20the%20farmers%20who%20are%20slaves%20to%20this%20Mukadam%20system%20(temporary%2C%20cheap%20labour)%2C%20of%20which%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Bombay%20took%20suo%20motu%20cognisance%20in%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20perils%20of%20this%20system%20extend%20beyond%20the%20direct%20victims%20%E2%80%94%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F417139%2Fhow-jasmine-transformed-tribal-lives-in-shahpur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20farmers%20who%20migrate%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20even%20spilling%20into%20their%20families.%20Women%20battle%20musculoskeletal%20disorders%20and%20gynaecological%20issues%3B%20teenage%20daughters%20are%20married%20off%20since%20they%20cannot%20be%20left%20alone%20in%20the%20villages%20while%20their%20parents%20are%20away%2C%20while%20younger%20children%20who%20accompany%20their%20parents%20to%20the%20sugarcane%20factories%20become%20victims%20of%20child%20labour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fpachega