%80%9D%20says%20Khan%2C%20as%20he%20carefully%20embroiders%20patterns%20on%20a%20tray%20shawl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20is%20the%20demand%20for%20his%20work%20that%20Khan%20does%20not%20believe%20in%20the%20market.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20huge%20demand%20for%20our%20items%2C%20but%20due%20to%20the%20shortage%20of%20skilled%20artisans%2C%20not%20many%20orders%20are%20accepted.%20We%20do%20not%20need%20the%20market%2C%20the%20market%20needs%20us%20because%20our%20patchwork%20Pashmina%20shawls%20are%20deeply%20appreciated%20and%20valued%20by%20our%20customers%2C%20who%20are%20willing%20to%20pay%20a%20good%20amount%20for%20them.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20fine%20Pashmina%20shawl%20with%20Jamawar%20patchwork%20is%20sold%20for%20Rs.%2015%2C000%2C%20making%20my%20job%20beyond%20imagination%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains%2C%20while%20dedicating%20himself%20to%20conserving%20the%20oldest%20form%20of%20Kashmiri%20shawl%20technique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-39_11zon-1748265016.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jamawar%20shawls%20aren%E2%80%99t%20just%20worn%20%E2%80%94%20they%E2%80%99re%20inherited.%20Each%20thread%20tells%20a%20story%20of%20Kashmiri%20heritage%20and%20timeless%20craft.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-39_11zon-1748265016.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-39_11zon-1748265016-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-39_11zon-1748265016-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-39_11zon-1748265016-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2F