entices.%20If%20I%20did%20not%20have%20patience%2C%20I%20would%20not%20have%20reintroduced%20the%20forgotten%20art%20of%20Jamawar%20shawl-making.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20septuagenarian%20claims%20that%2C%20to%20this%20day%2C%20there%20is%20not%20a%20single%20artisan%20in%20the%20Valley%20who%20can%20create%20Jamawar%20patchwork%20on%20shawls%20as%20he%20does.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20can%20do%20Jamawar%20work%20like%20I%20do.%20Though%20I%20have%20trained%20many%20people%20in%20the%20past%2C%20including%20my%20brother%2C%20they%20lack%20the%20accuracy%20and%20dedication%20required%20for%20this%20craft.%20I%20would%20be%20over%20the%20moon%20to%20see%20artisans%20stepping%20into%20my%20shoes%2C%20and%20they%20would%20also%20get%20all%20the%20awards%20I%20receive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Khan%2C%20another%20reason%20Jamawar%20work%20has%20struggled%20to%20progress%20is%20the%20declining%20respect%20for%20handicrafts%20in%20Kashmir.%20A%20growing%20craze%20for%20white-collar%20jobs%20has%20led%20many%20to%20look%20down%20on%20traditional%20artisan%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Director%20of%20Handicrafts%20and%20Handloom%20Kashmir%2C%20Mussarat%20Islam%2C%20tells%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20432%20centres%20across%20Kashmir%20are%20currently%20functioning%20under%20the%20department%2C%20where%20various%20traditional%20art%20forms%2C%20including%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20Jamawar%20patchwork%2C%20are%20officially%20recognised%20and%20taught.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20each%20centre%2C%20skilled%20artisans%2C%20including%204%20to%205%20master%20craftsmen%20like%20Khan%20are%20training%20budding%20artists%20who%20also%20receive%20stipends%20and%20allowances%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20further%20promote%20Jamawar%20patchwork%2C%20we%20are%20actively%20introducing%20it%20under%20various%20government%20schemes%20aimed%20at%20preserving%20and%20expanding%20this%20heritage%20craft.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%