%20(DID)%2C%20where%20someone%20has%20different%20identity%20states.%20But%20schizophrenia%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20%E2%80%98split%20personalities%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr.%20Khanna%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Shweta%20Sharma%20elaborates%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20most%20common%20and%20misleading%20myths%20in%20India%20is%20that%20schizophrenia%20means%20%E2%80%98split%20personality.%E2%80%99%20This%20confusion%20leads%20to%20stigma%2C%20fear%2C%20and%20delayed%20treatment.%20But%20let%E2%80%99s%20set%20the%20record%20straight.%20Schizophrenia%20is%20a%20chronic%2C%20severe%20mental%20health%20condition%20that%20affects%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20thoughts%2C%20emotions%2C%20and%20behaviours.%20It%20involves%20psychotic%20symptoms%20like%20hallucinations%2C%20delusions%2C%20disorganised%20thinking%2C%20social%20withdrawal%2C%20and%20flattened%20affect.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20schizophrenia%2C%20the%20core%20disturbance%20is%20in%20reality%20orientation%2C%20the%20person%20often%20loses%20touch%20with%20reality.%20This%20impaired%20reality%20testing%20is%20a%20key%20feature%2C%20and%20it%20can%20affect%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETime%20orientation%20(confused%20about%20day%2Ftime)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPlace%20orientation%20(unsure%20where%20they%20are)%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPerson%20orientation%20(mistrust%20or%20misidentification%20of%20others)%2C%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESituation%20orientation%20(misinterpreting%20context%2C%20such%20as%20thinking%20they%20are%20in%20danger%20when%20they%20are%20not)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20Dissociative%20Identity%20Disorder%20(DID)%2C%20which%20people%20mistakenly%20refer%20to%20as%20%E2%80%9Csplit%20personality%E2%80%9D%2C%20involves%20two%20or%20more%20distinct%20identities%20or%20personality%20states%20that%20alternate%20in%20controlling%20the%20individual%E2%80%99s%20behavior.%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20schizophrenia%20is%20not%20about%20%E2%80%98having%20two%20minds.%E2%80%99%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20a%20disruption%20in%20perceiving%20and%20processing%20reality.%20That%20distinction%20is%20crucial%20for%20both%20clinical%20understanding%20and%20reducing%20stigma%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-05-23-at-5.01.47-PM-1747999927-500x750.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20might%20confuse%20schizophrenia%20with%20having%20a%20split%20personality.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-05-23-at-5.01.47-PM-1747999927-500x750.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-05-23-at-5.01.47-PM-1747999927-200x300.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-05-23-at-5.01.47-PM-1747999927-768x1152.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-05-23-at-5.01.47-PM-1747999927-150x225.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-05-23-at-5.01.47-PM-1747999927.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-437569%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOne%20might%20confuse%20schizophrenia%20with%20having%20a%20split%20personality.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThink%20of%20it%20this%20way%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F436280%2Ffather-daughter-schizophrenia-mental-health-law-reform-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20person%20with%20schizophrenia%20may%20hear%20voices%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20aren%E2%80%99t%20there%20or%20believe%20things%20that%20others%20don%E2%80%99t%2C%20like%20feeling%20watched%20when%20they%E2%80%99re%20not.%20It%20affects%20how%20someone%20understands%20and%20responds%20to%20reality.%20But%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%9Cswitch%20personalities%E2%80%9D%20or%20become%20someone%20else%20entirely%2C%20as%20often%20shown%20in%20films%20or%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20confusion%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20harmless%20mix-up%20%E2%80%94%20it%20changes%20how%20we%20see%20people.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20people%20think%20%E2%80%98split%20personality%2C%E2%80%99%20they%20assume%20instability%20or%20danger%2C%20and%20that%20makes%20stigma%20worse%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr.%20Khanna%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20stigma%20can%20be%20damaging.%20It%20can%20isolate%20people%2C%20prevent%20them%20from%20seeking%20help%2C%20and%20deepen%20the%20fear%20around%20something%20that%E2%80%99s%20already%20misunderstood.%20Understanding%20the%20difference%20is%20the%20first%20step%20to%20treating%20people%20with%20empathy%2C%20not%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMyth%202%3A%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20with%20schizophrenia%20are%20always%20dangerous%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMovies%20often%20show%20people%20with%20schizophrenia%20as%20violent%20or%20unpredictable%20%E2%80%94%20someone%20lashing%20out%2C%20losing%20control%2C%20or%20whispering%20to%20themselves%20before%20