2C%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20fort%20has%20seen%20everything%20from%20sieges%20and%20dynasties%20to%20deaths%20and%20miracles.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20walked%20through%20a%20maze%20of%20broken%20rooms%2C%20old%20granaries%2C%20and%20ancient%20reservoirs.%20The%20stone%20under%20my%20feet%20felt%20charged%20as%20if%20it%20remembered%20the%20rhythm%20of%20royal%20processions%2C%20war%20drums%2C%20and%20temple%20bells.%20%E2%80%9CHammir%20Dev%20Chauhan%20ruled%20from%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Imtiyaz%20told%20me.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20fought%20Alauddin%20Khilji%E2%80%99s%20army%20till%20the%20very%20end.%20According%20to%20legend%2C%20his%20queen%20committed%20Jauhar%20(jumping%20into%20a%20fire)%20right%20here%2C%20in%20these%20ruins%2C%20to%20escape%20capture%2C%20and%20his%20unmarried%20daughter%20in%20the%20reservoir.%E2%80%9D%20His%20story%20narration%20was%20beautiful%2C%20taking%20me%20back%20in%20time%2C%20and%20I%20could%20feel%20goosebumps%20all%20over%20my%20body.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20long%20walk%20and%20many%20stories%2C%20we%20reached%20the%20top%2C%20and%20from%20there%2C%20we%20could%20see%20the%20panoramic%20views%20of%20the%20surrounding%20landscape.%20The%20view%20was%20staggering%3A%20the%20green%20expanse%20of%20%3Cstrong%3ERanthambore%20National%20Park%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20the%20shimmering%20waters%20of%20Padam%20Talao.%20It%20was%20easy%20to%20see%20why%20this%20stronghold%20was%20so%20coveted%20by%20rulers%20throughout%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FStairs-and-fort-entrance_11zon-1748149197.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Weathered%20stone%20steps%20and%20shadowy%20arches%20welcome%20you%20into%20the%20fort's%20embrace%2C%20where%20every%20turn%20carries%20echoes%20of%20the%20past.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FStairs-and-fort-entrance_11zon-1748149197.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FStairs-and-fort-entrance_11zon-1748149197-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FStairs-and-fort-entrance_11zon-1748149197-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FStairs-and-fort-entrance_11zon-1748149197-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FStairs-and-fort-entrance_11zon-1748149197-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-438439%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWeathered%20stone%20steps%20and%20shadowy%20arches%20welcome%20you%20into%20the%20fort%E2%80%99s%20embrace%2C%20where%20every%20turn%20carries%20echoes%20of%20the%20past.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weathered%20walls%2C%20punctuated%20by%20massive%20gates%20like%20Hathi%20Pol%20and%20Ganesh%20Pol%2C%20bore%20the%20marks%20of%20time%20and%20countless%20sieges.%20As%20I%20wandered%20through%20the%20crumbling%20structures%2C%20imagining%20the%20armies%20that%20once%20marched%20through%20these%20very%20gateways%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20tangible%20connection%20to%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20rich%20and%20often%20turbulent%20past.%20The%20architecture%2C%20a%20fascinating%20mix%20of%20Rajput%20and%20Mughal%20styles%2C%20spoke%20volumes%20about%20the%20different%20eras%20and%20influences%20that%20had%20shaped%20this%20formidable%20citadel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20moment%2C%20I%20stood%20still%2C%20silenced%20by%20the%20scale%20of%20it%20all.%20I%20had%20come%20to%20Ranthambore%20looking%20for%20something%20wild.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20it%20would%20begin%20with%20stone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETrinetra%20Ganesh%20Temple%3A%20Devotion%20carved%20in%20stone%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHigh%20atop%20the%20fort%2C%20nestled%20within%20a%20quiet%20courtyard%2C%20we%20reached%20the%20%3Cstrong%3ETrinetra%20Ganesh%20Temple%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20small%20shrine%20that%20exuded%20an%20almost%20tangible%20aura%20of%20faith.%20I%20had%20heard%20whispers%20of%20its%20legend%20even%20before%20I%20began%20the%20climb%3A%20that%20during%20a%20siege%20in%201299%20by%20Alauddin%20Khilji%E2%80%99s%20forces%2C%20King%20Hammir%20Dev%20Chauhan%2C%20a%20devout%20follower%20of%20Lord%20Ganesh%2C%20had%20a%20dream.%20In%20it%2C%20Ganesh%20promised%20that%20his%20troubles%20would%20be%20over%20by%20dawn.%20The%20next%20morning%2C%20a%20self-manifested%20idol%20of%20Ganesh%20with%20three%20eyes%20(Trinetra)%20was%20discovered%20within%20the%20fort.%20Soon%20after%2C%20the%20siege%20inexplicably%20lifted.%20The%20idol%20remained%2C%20and%20so%20did%20the%20belief.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20sanctum%2C%20the%20air%20felt%20cool%20and%20still.%20The%20Trinetra%20idol%2C%20flanked%20by%20his%20consorts%20Riddhi%20and%20Siddhi%20and%20sons%20Shubh%20and%20Labh%2C%20exuded%20a%20quiet%20serenity.%20It%20is%20said%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20few%20temples%20in%20the%20world%20that%20depicts%20Lord%20Ganesh%20in%20this%20complete%20familial%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2