n%20have%20a%20dedicated%20postbox%20for%20Lord%20Ganesh.%E2%80%9D%20He%20smiled%20and%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20yes%2C%20the%20postman%20does%20deliver%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20something%20profoundly%20moving%20about%20that.%20In%20a%20world%20of%20fleeting%20rituals%2C%20here%20was%20a%20practice%20rooted%20in%20belief%2C%20blessing%2C%20and%20the%20quiet%20hope%20that%20beginnings%20like%20marriages%20deserve%20divine%20acknowledgement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStanding%20there%2C%20I%20thought%20the%20rugged%20stone%20walls%20of%20the%20fort%2C%20which%20had%20once%20echoed%20with%20the%20cries%20of%20war%20and%20conquest%2C%20now%20stood%20silent%20witness%20to%20centuries%20of%20devotion.%20It%20struck%20me%20then%20that%20Ranthambore%20Fort%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F401836%2Findian-currency-money-features-indian-monuments-konark-temple-hampi-chariot%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehistorical%20monument%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20a%20breathing%2C%20believing%20space.%20A%20place%20where%20faith%20had%20outlasted%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20place%20that%20stays%20with%20you%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20descended%20from%20the%20fort%2C%20the%20jungle%20began%20to%20rise%20again%20in%20the%20distance.%20But%20something%20had%20shifted.%20I%20had%20come%20to%20Ranthambore%20hoping%20to%20lock%20eyes%20with%20a%20tiger%2C%20to%20chase%20that%20fleeting%20thrill%20of%20the%20wild%2C%20which%20I%20did%20during%20my%20safari.%20And%20yet%2C%20it%20was%20the%20fort%2C%20not%20the%20forest%2C%20that%20had%20captured%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FView-from-the-fort_11zon-1748149622.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22From%20the%20fort%E2%80%99s%20summit%2C%20Padam%20Talao%20sparkles%20below%E2%80%94a%20mirror%20to%20the%20wild%20and%20a%20reminder%20of%20how%20history%20and%20nature%20intertwine%20in%20Ranthambore.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FView-from-the-fort_11zon-1748149622.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FView-from-the-fort_11zon-1748149622-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FView-from-the-fort_11zon-1748149622-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FView-from-the-fort_11zon-1748149622-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FView-from-the-fort_11zon-1748149622-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-438444%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFrom%20the%20fort%E2%80%99s%20summit%2C%20Padam%20Talao%20sparkles%20below%20%E2%80%94%20a%20mirror%20to%20the%20wild%20and%20a%20reminder%20of%20how%20history%20and%20nature%20intertwine%20in%20Ranthambore.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20at%20the%20resort%2C%20the%20calm%20returned.%20Sitting%20on%20my%20cottage%20verandah%20with%20the%20forest%20humming%20gently%20around%20me%2C%20I%20realised%20the%20fort%20had%20given%20me%20something%20the%20jungle%20hadn%E2%80%99t%E2%80%94a%20sense%20of%20time%20paused%2C%20of%20faith%20held%20steady%20across%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20dinner%2C%20a%20staff%20member%20smiled%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20fort%20watches%20everything.%20Even%20the%20tigers%20know%20it.%E2%80%9D%20And%20I%20believed%20him.%20In%20Ranthambore%2C%20the%20wild%20is%20not%20just%20in%20the%20jungle.%20It%E2%80%99s%20in%20the%20legends%20whispered%20through%20stone%2C%20in%20temples%20that%20receive%20wedding%20invitations%20by%20post%2C%20and%20in%20customs%20and%20beliefs%20passed%20down%20through%20generations.%20I%20came%20looking%20for%20a%20predator%2C%20but%20I%20found%20something%20else%3A%20a%20stillness%2C%20a%20strength%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20wonder%20I%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20expected.%20And%20that%2C%20I%20realised%2C%20is%20the%20real%20magic%20of%20Ranthambore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Leila%20Badyari%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748161800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D438427%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20came%20in%20search%20of%20the%20elusive%20tiger%2C%20but%20it%20was%20the%20ancient%20fort%20with%20its%20forgotten%20legends%20and%20quiet%20power%20that%20truly%20left%20its%20mark.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shweta%20Dravid%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F438427%2Fbeyond-tigers-ranthambore-fort-history-safari-stories%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20an%20Architect%20Turned%20a%20Dusty%20Abandoned%20Mumbai%20Warehouse%20Into%20a%20Home%20for%20the%20Arts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20warm%20afternoon%20in%20Mumbai%3B%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20mercury%20levels%20are%20setting%20new%20benchmarks%20every%20day.%20But%20even%20as%20Mumbai%20sweats%2C%20a%20certain%20room%20in%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20Shakti%20Mills%20neighbourhood%20appears%20to%20be%20immune%2C%20both%20to%20the%20heat%20and%20the%20cosmopolitanism%20brewing%20outside%20its%20perimeters.%20The%20%E2%80%98Black%20Box%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20India%20%E2%80%94%20(the%20room%E2%80%99s%20aesthetic%20mimics%20its%20moniker)%20is%20an%20architecturally%20striking%20oasis%20of%20cool.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20the%20room%20could%20speak%2C%20it%20would%20argue%20that%2C%20ever%20so%20often%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20flooded%20with%20warmth%20in%20the%20form%20of%20conversations%20that%20are%20born%20here.%20You%20see%2C%20the%20Black%20Box%20nestled%20in%20G5A%20%E2%80%94%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20very%20own%20album%20of%20contemporary%20art%2C%20is%20a%20multi-functional%20space%20that%20plays%20host%20to%20screenings%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F318825%2Fpune-dancer-helps-parkinsons-disease-patients-with-free-dance-therapy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperformances%20and%20plays%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai-based%20architect%20and%20filmmaker%20Anuradha%20Parikh%20charts%20the%20course%20of%20transforming%20a%20once%20humble%20warehouse%20in%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Shakti%20Mills%20into%20its%20current%20identity%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98home%20for%20experimental%20and%20independent%20arts%E2%80%99.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20process%2C%20the%20space%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20had%20metamorphosed.%20Parikh%20had%2C%20too.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A0%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faarohan.infosys.org%2F%3Fcmpid%3Dsco_TheBetterIndia_EB_AarohanAwards25_foundation_banner_24042025_lq_Awareness_Rgn%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fg5a-warehouse-2-1747926728.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Black%20Box%20is%20a%20unique%2C%20multifunctional%20space%20that%20presents%20screenings%2C%20conversations%2C%20performances%2C%20presentations%2C%20workshops%2C%20and%20courses%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fg5a-warehouse-2-1747926728.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fg5a-warehouse-2-1747926728-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fg5a-warehouse-2-1747926728-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fg5a-warehouse-2-1747926728-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fg5a-warehouse-2-1747926728-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-437095%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Black%20Box%20is%20a%20unique%2C%20multifunctional%20space%20that%20presents%20screenings%2C%20conversations%2C%20performances%2C%20presentations%2C%20workshops%2C%20and%20courses%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20G5A%20stands%20against%20the%20cityline%20as%20a%20pi%C3%A8ce%20de%20r%C3%A9sistance%20for%20the%20contemporary%20arts%2C%20daring%20urbanity%20to%20challenge%20its%20ideals.%20Through%20its%20repertoire%20of%20screenings%2C%20conversations%20and%20theatre%20festivals%2C%20it%20is%20furthering%20the%20legacy%20of%20the%20artistic%20movement%20that%20enveloped%20Mumbai%20in%20a%20tight%20embrace%20from%20the%201960s%20through%20the%201980s.%20To%20Parikh%2C%20the%20Black%20Box%20is%20a%20metaphor%20for%20potential%2C%20for%20infinite%20possibility.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20black%20void%2C%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20any%20specific%20form%2C%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20boundaries.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20recalls%20the%20conundrum%20of%20finding%20a%20middle%20ground%20between%20wanting%20to%20redesign%20completely%20and%20wanting%20to%20preserve%20the%20antiquity%20of%20the%20warehouse.%20Finally%2C%20her%20design%20philosophy%20leaned%20towards%20the%20latter.%20But%20the%20premise%20was%20always%20inclusion.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20want%20this%20to%20become%20just%20a%20venue%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366709%2Fkamal-malik-ballard-estate-ambico-ice-factory-restoration-if-be-cultural-centre%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espace%20that%20would%20be%20accessible%20for%20local%20communities%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Our%20tagline%20%E2%80%98culture%2C%20community%2C%20and%20city%E2%80%99%20gives%20an%20essence%20of%20what%20G5A%20was%20meant%20to%20be%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20art%20and%20community%20convene%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EReserved%20for%20VIPs%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20words%20are%20sometimes%20plastered%20on%20the%20front-row%20seats%20at%20programmes%20at%20G5A.%20Guests%20filing%20in%20leave%20the%20seats%20vacant%2C%20which%20soon%20seat%20their%20lawful%20occupants%20%E2%80%94%20the%20millworkers%2C%20the%20Kolis%2C%20members%20of%20the%20Worli%20Koliwada%20sea-faring%20community%2C%20and%20others%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20these%20programmes%2C%20they%20are%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmissing%20VIPs%E2%80%9D%2C%20Parikh%20points%20out.%20This%20thought%20aligns%20with%20her%20intent%20of%20making%20the%20local%20communities%20important%20stakeholders%20of%20the%20G5A%20mission.%20%E2%80%9CArt%20enables%20us%20to%20think%20differently%2C%20shifts%20something%20in%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20emphasises.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20empowers%20us%20to%20redefine%20how%20we%20live%20our%20lives%2C%20how%20we%20vote%20(from%20Leonard%20Bernstein%E2%80%99s%20quote%20that%20is%20mounted%20on%20one%20of%20their%20walls)%2C%20and%20gives%20us%20a%20kit%20for%20life.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParikh%E2%80%99s%20familiarity%20with%20contemporary%20art%20disciplines%20borrows%20from%20her%20parents.%20Her%20mother%2C%20Shaila%20Mohile%20Parikh%2C%20founded%20the%20famed%20Mohile%20Parikh%20Centre%20%E2%80%94%20an%20internationally%20renowned%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F300577%2Fbest-folk-artists-and-artisans-take-masterclasses-on-first-culture-tech-platform-memeraki%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstitution%20devoted%20to%20art%20and%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20NCPA%20(National%20Centre%20for%20the%20Performing%20Arts)%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20while%20her%20father%2C%20Jagdish%20Parikh%2C%20was%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Film%20Finance%20Corporation%20(%E2%80%9Cwhich%20he%20redefined%20as%20the%20National%20Film%20Development%20Corporation%E2%80%9D).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParikh%E2%80%99s%20childhood%20and%20youth%20were%20filled%20with%20encounters%20with%20the%20likes%20of%20Shyam%20Benegal%20(also%20known%20as%20the%20pioneer%20of%20parallel%20Indian%20cinema)%20Mani%20Kaul%2C%20Kumar%20Shahani%2C%20renowned%20artists%20M%20F%20Husain%2C%20Akbar%20Padamsee%2C%20Nalini%20Malani%2C%20Raza%2C%20famed%20classical%20musicians%20Vilayat%20Khan%2C%20Bhimsain%20Joshi%2C%20Shobha%20Gurtu%2C%20and%20visionary%20architects%20Charles%20Correa%20and%20B%20V%20Doshi.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20privileged%20to%20grow%20up%20in%20that%20environment%2C%20with%20all%20of%20these%20artists%20as%20a%20kind%20of%20extended%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parikh%20points%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20deep%20respect%20for%20art%20was%20part%20of%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20lingua%20franca.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22G5A%20was%20repurposed%20from%20a%20space%20that%20served%20as%20a%20warehouse%20for%20mill%20workers%20to%20now%20a%20thriving%20space%20for%20culture%20and%20arts%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447-800x600.jpeg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447-600x450.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447-400x300.jpeg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447-200x150.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-437087%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EG5A%20was%20repurposed%20from%20a%20space%20that%20served%20as%20a%20warehouse%20for%20mill%20workers%20to%20now%20a%20thriving%20space%20for%20culture%20and%20arts%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20during%20the%201970s%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F127452%2Findependent-cinema-bollywood-2017-unconventional-films-crowdfunding-self-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewave%20of%20alternative%20cinema%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20steadily%20picking%20up.%20The%20movement%E2%80%99s%20genius%20lay%20in%20its%20realism%20and%20complex%20themes.%20The%20filmmakers%20during%20this%20time%20brought%20style%20and%20substance%20to%20the%20rhetoric%2C%20allowing%20societal%20issues%20to%20be%20viewed%20from%20a%20nuanced%20lens.%20But%20in%20the%20decades%20that%20followed%2C%20this%20cinematic%20brilliance%20was%20wrestled%20from%20the%20city%20by%20commercial%20mainstream%20movies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMumbai%E2%80%99s%20seams%20began%20bursting%20with%20urban%20development%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parikh%20puts%20the%20case%20into%20point%20as%20she%20speaks%20of%20how%20this%20increased%20the%20pressure%20on%20art%20and%20artists.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20evolution%20of%20Bombay%2C%20art%20became%20a%20victi